import React from 'react';
import { TextField, Button, FormControl, Grid, Container, Typography } from '@mui/material';

const JefeView = () => {
  return (
    <Container maxWidth="sm">
      <Typography variant="h4" align="center" gutterBottom>
        Vista del Jefe
      </Typography>

      <FormControl fullWidth margin="normal">
        <Grid container spacing={2}>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <TextField
              label="No. de Tela"
              variant="outlined"
              fullWidth
              required
            />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <TextField
              label="Talla"
              variant="outlined"
              fullWidth
              required
            />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <TextField
              label="Color"
              variant="outlined"
              fullWidth
              required
            />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <TextField
              label="Estilo"
              variant="outlined"
              fullWidth
              required
            />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <TextField
              label="Estado"
              variant="outlined"
              fullWidth
              required
            />
          </Grid>
        </Grid>

        <Grid container spacing={2} justifyContent="center" marginTop={2}>
          <Grid item>
            <Button variant="contained" color="primary">
              Guardar
            </Button>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item>
            <Button variant="outlined" color="secondary">
              Imprimir Reportes
            </Button>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </FormControl>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default JefeView;
